## Prediction OTel Spans

### Prediction Span (`wasm4pm.prediction`)
```
pm.prediction.target     = "remaining_time" | "next_activity" | "outcome" | "sla_violation"
pm.prediction.value      = <numeric result>
pm.prediction.confidence = 0.0–1.0
pm.prediction.model_name = "ngram-markov" | "weibull" | "anomaly-dfg"
pm.algorithm.name        = "extract_case_features"
pm.algorithm.duration_ms = 7.0
pm.log.format            = "xes"
```

### Git Ingestion Span (`wasm4pm.git.commit`)
```
git.commit.sha        = "8a20902"
git.commit.type       = "feat"           ← XES concept:name
git.commit.scope      = "prediction"
git.commit.is_breaking = false
git.branch.name       = "main"           ← XES case:id
git.author.email      = "dev@example.com"
```

### GitHub PR Span (`wasm4pm.github.pr_lifecycle`)
```
github.pr.number       = 14              ← XES case:id
github.pr.state        = "pr:merged"     ← XES concept:name
github.pr.cycle_time_ms = 5400000.0
github.workflow.status = "success"
github.release.tag     = "v26.4.5"
```

## Prediction → Prescription Flow

```
extract_case_features (7ms)
  └─ pm.prediction.target = "remaining_time"
  └─ pm.prediction.confidence = 0.85
  └─► pm.prescription.action = "escalate"
      pm.prescription.rationale = "High SLA violation risk"
      pm.prescription.impact = "risk_mitigation"
```

